description: Out of the blue, Joseph gets Delirious Hunter a special gift for no particular occasion. It's a ride-on sex machine called "The Tremor" and it redefines "Rock And Roll"! After learning how to use the controls, Delirious hops on board for the ride of her life. To show her appreciation, she gives Joey a magnificent blow job while she comes to many screaming orgasms!
title: The Gift That Keeps On Giving: The Tremor
